OL,3,CNew stamps issue celebrates 'skill,
OL,4,Cambition and design' of castles
OL,6,FRoyal Mail has unveiled images of a
OL,7,Fnew set of stamps featuring a number
OL,8,Fof castles across the UK.
OL,10,FThe stamps depict photographs of eight
OL,11,Fcastles, dating from the Norman period
OL,12,Fonwards ` Dunluce, Dundrum, Raglan,
OL,13,FPembroke, Urquhart, Stirling, Warwick
OL,14,Fand Bamburgh.
OL,16,FA further four stamps presented in a
OL,17,Fminiature sheet celebrate royal
OL,18,Fcastles at Caernarfon, Windsor, Dover
OL,19,Fand Balmoral. They are commissioned
OL,20,Fartworks by British illustrator Rob
OL,21,FBall.
