OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778746039
OL,3,CNew stamps issue celebrates 'skill,
OL,4,Cambition and design' of castles
OL,6,FDavid Gold, director of external
OL,7,Faffairs and policy at Royal Mail,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Castles are among the most
OL,9,Frecognisable features of the UK's
OL,10,Flandscape, and this stamp issue
OL,11,Fcelebrates the skill, ambition and
OL,12,Fdesign, as well as the durability,
OL,13,Fbehind these remarkable structures
OL,14,Ffrom across the nations."
OL,16,FThe stamps, and a range of collectible
OL,17,Fproducts, are available to pre-order
OL,18,Ffrom Thursday and will go on general
OL,19,Fsale from May 21.
